  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate post-mastectomy breast skin blood supply (perfusion)&#xD;
      after radiation therapy, and before and after fat grafting to the breast(s).&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
